                        <h4>Australian Shepherd</h4>
                        <p><strong>Temperament:</strong> Smart, Work-Oriented, Exuberant</p>
                        <p><strong>Height:</strong> 20-23 inches (male), 18-21 inches (female)</p>
                        <p><strong>Weight:</strong> 50-65 pounds (male), 40-55 pounds (female)</p>
                        <p><strong>Life Expectancy:</strong> 12-15 years</p>
                        <p><strong>Group:</strong> Herding</p>
                    </div>
