                    <div class="col-sm">
                        <br>
                        <br>
                        <p>The australian shepherd, nicknamed the aussie, is a medium-sized herding breed. They are known for their intelligence and endurance. There are multiple coat colors that an aussie can have. Otis has a tri-color coat, being black, white and brown. </p>
